"MetaModelica,Modelica and C/C++ are available with syntax highlighting "
"and autocompletion of keywords and types. Additionaly the Modelica and "
"MetaModelica files are provided with autocompletion of code-snippets "
"along with keywords and types. The users can load the directory from file"
" menu *File > Open Directory*. which opens the Directory structure in the"
" Libraries-browser."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/omedit.rst:1573
